    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《苍空之韵》作为一款把飞行射击类游戏和音乐节奏玩法融合的游戏，在设计上进行了一些大胆的创新。希望玩家可以在享受飞行射击类游戏的过程中跟着音乐节奏来获得一种独特的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，游戏里还有多种武器攻玩家自由搭配来进行攻击手段上的改变。此外，装备系统也拥有足够的养成搭配玩法。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【故事内容】</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要扮演一对姐妹逃脱同门的追杀来解开被栽赃的谜团。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【新颖的战斗系统】</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/ff71a997f16e1542c468f7f7dbd2db9e.poster.avif?t=1740462871\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/ff71a997f16e1542c468f7f7dbd2db9e.webm?t=1740462871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/ff71a997f16e1542c468f7f7dbd2db9e.mp4?t=1740462871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据音乐的节奏点来进行攻击与技能释放的操作。节奏点踩的越准，技能效果越强。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【自由搭配的法宝系统】</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/b14bade729398f0c4b5109ceb3b1d51d.poster.avif?t=1740462871\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/b14bade729398f0c4b5109ceb3b1d51d.webm?t=1740462871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/b14bade729398f0c4b5109ceb3b1d51d.mp4?t=1740462871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以自由选择自己的副法宝更换自己的攻击手段。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【韵石套装系统】</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/4ab47a8f6aece96be36bfe686e39e678.poster.avif?t=1740462871\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/4ab47a8f6aece96be36bfe686e39e678.webm?t=1740462871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229940/extras/4ab47a8f6aece96be36bfe686e39e678.mp4?t=1740462871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持2件套和4件套效果自由搭配多种策略。</p>",
